<http://status.aws.amazon.com/|Informational message: Call quality degradation>
We are investigating degraded call quality in the US-EAST-1 Region.

<http://status.aws.amazon.com/|Service is operating normally: [RESOLVED] Call quality degradation>
Between 7:10 AM and 8:55 AM PDT, we experienced degraded call quality in the US-EAST-1 Region. Agents and end-customers may have experienced increased call latency or static on calls during this time. The issue has been resolved and the service is operating normally.
